type at a glance — a job, a customer, a part, a lead, an asset, or an expense."},{"label":"Title","value":"The main label: a job number, customer name, part number, company name, asset name, or expense description."},{"label":"Subtitle","value":"A bit more context underneath, such as the job title, company name, part description, contact name, serial number, or expense category. Sometimes it's blank."},{"label":"Type label","value":"A small tag telling you whether it's a Job, Customer, Part, Lead, Asset, or Expense, so you can spot the right one fast."},{"label":"Where it takes you","value":"Clicking a result opens that record's details right over its list, and the details stay in the web address so you can bookmark or share the link. Expenses are the exception — they just open the Expenses list."}]},{"heading":"Keyboard Shortcuts","items":[{"label":"Ctrl+K","value":"Jumps to the search box from anywhere in the app, on any page. It's the only keyboard shortcut for search."},{"label":"Click outside","value":"Clicking outside the box closes the results (with a tiny pause so a result click still counts). It leaves your typed text in place."},{"label":"Click a result","value":"Takes you to that record and opens its details (expenses open their list instead), then closes the results. The box clears itself."}]},{"heading":"AI Results (when the AI helper is on)","items":[{"label":"Two columns","value":"When the AI helper is on, the results split into two columns: the plain text matches on the left and AI results on the right."},{"label":"Written answer","value":"A short answer to your question in plain language, marked with a lightbulb. The AI helper writes it for you."},{"label":"Matching snippets","value":"Bits of related content pulled from your records. Each snippet shows the text, where it came from, its type, and how good a match it is as a percentage."},{"label":"Match score","value":"A percentage showing how closely a snippet fits the meaning of your question. Higher means a better match."},{"label":"Thinking spinner","value":"A little spinner with 'Thinking...' shows while the AI helper works on your question. AI results can take a touch longer than the plain text ones."},{"label":"If AI is off","value":"If the AI helper isn't running, you simply get the single column of text matches. Nothing breaks and no error shows — search just keeps working without it."}]},{"heading":"Good to Know","items":[{"label":"You must be signed in","value":"Search only works when you're logged in, the same as the rest of the app."},{"label":"At least 2 letters","value":"Nothing is searched until you've typed 2 letters. Extra spaces around your words are ignored."},{"label":"Upper or lower case is fine","value":"Case doesn't matter, and it matches anywhere in the text — searching 'gear' finds 'Gearbox Housing'."},{"label":"A fair mix of results","value":"You'll get a balanced spread across the types instead of one type filling the whole list, with the most recently updated records shown first."},{"label":"Newest first within a type","value":"Within each type, the records you touched most recently show up first, so recent work is easy to find."},{"label":"Archived items are hidden","value":"Deleted records never show up, and archived jobs are left out of search too."}]}]}"""
        });

        // ── Knowledge Check (Quiz) ───────────────────────────────────────
        await GetOrCreateModule(new TrainingModule
